The paper deals with generating context-aware captions for images, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of inference techniques and discriminative models, which are common in the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
